  "texts": [
    "For efficient data observation, real-time visualization (demonstrated in Fig. 7) of the collected sensor data was applied to monitor the quality of the gathered data.",
    "Using this approach, the research team was able to identify any instances of sensor disconnection or poor attachment, as well as to detect drift in the IMU.",
    "In fact, some participants experienced such disruptions during the collection process, necessitating additional data collection.",
    "The data collection process is summarized in Table 4.",
    "First, the participants were briefed regarding the types of sensors they would be wearing, the number and types of strokes to be performed, and relevant instructions well in advance."
  ]
}